  <scopecontent id="aspace_72ba6871bc111078c825136668aca4f0">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence files dealing with requests for books as well as cancellations of request, and letters denoting request or shipment errors. Also included are information bulletins, technical memos, minutes of library department meetings, the 1964-65 Book Budget, a Catalogue Procedures Manual, and payroll carbons from the Industrial and Labor Relations library. 1963-64 monthly reports, sample acquisition forms, and special non-heading orders are also included.</p>  </scopecontent>
